 flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼo">&lt;form</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">method</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"POST"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">enctype</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"multipart/form-data"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"text"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"headline"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">placeholder</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"Headline"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"file"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"image"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;textarea</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"content"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;button</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"submit"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><span>Submit</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/form&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="626" data-end="698">👉 Important:<br>
<code data-start="640" data-end="671">enctype="multipart/form-data"</code> = required for file upload</p>
<hr data-start="700" data-end="703">
<h2 data-section-id="mec7d4" data-start="705" data-end="729">PHP part (basic idea)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="731" data-end="874"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>$image = $_FILES['image']['name'];</span><br><span>$tmp_name = $_FILES['image']['tmp_name'];</span><br><br><span>move_uploaded_file($tmp_name, "../uploads/" . $image);</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="1j23gtg" data-start="876" data-end="896">What this means:</h3>
<ul data-start="898" data-end="1048">
<li data-section-id="v4h41p" data-start="898" data-end="941">
<p data-start="900" data-end="941"><code data-start="900" data-end="909">$_FILES</code> → contains uploaded file info</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15580az" data-start="942" data-end="982">
<p data-start="944" data-end="982"><code data-start="944" data-end="954">tmp_name</code> → temporary file location</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rs42qx" data-start="983" data-end="1048">
<p data-start="985" data-end="1048"><code data-start="985" data-end="1007">move_uploaded_file()</code> → moves file to your <code data-start="1029" data-end="1039">uploads/</code> folder</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1050" data-end="1053">
<h2 data-section-id="4wzkxw" data-start="1055" data-end="1084">Database stores only this:</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1086" data-end="1116"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>uploads/image1.jpg</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1139">NOT the actual image.</p>
<hr data-start="1141" data-end="1144">
<h2 data-section-id="urbmaw" data-start="1146" data-end="1164">Then on website</h2>
<p data-start="1166" data-end="1180">To show image:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1182" data-end="1241"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼo">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"uploads/</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">echo</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'image'</span><span>]; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span class="ͼk">"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1243" data-end="1246">
<h2 data-section-id="jpdk7f" data-start="1248" data-end="1285">Simple explanation (for interview)</h2>
<p data-start="1287" data-end="1299">You can say:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1301" data-end="1488">
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1488">The admin uploads an image using a form. PHP receives the file, stores it in a server folder, and saves the file path in the database. The frontend then loads the image using that path.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1490" data-end="1493">
<p data-start="1495" data-end="1519">If you want, next I can:</p>
<ul data-start="1520" data-end="1658" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="6cpp32" data-start="1520" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1522" data-end="1566">Walk you line-by-line through image upload</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15nasef" data-start="1567" data-end="1658" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1569" data-end="1658" data-is-last-node="">Or help you build your first working <code data-start="1606" data-end="1620">add-news.php</code> step by step (no copy paste learning)</p>
</li>
