<p data-start="68" data-end="113">Let’s make it <strong data-start="82" data-end="97">very simple</strong>, no code first.</p>
<hr data-start="115" data-end="118">
<h2 data-section-id="yyg2w8" data-start="120" data-end="165">🔹 What is “upload image” in your project?</h2>
<p data-start="167" data-end="180">Imagine this:</p>
<ol data-start="182" data-end="299">
<li data-section-id="r825a0" data-start="182" data-end="212">
<p data-start="185" data-end="212">Your boss opens admin panel</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10o1m9q" data-start="213" data-end="240">
<p data-start="216" data-end="240">Clicks <strong data-start="223" data-end="240">“Choose File”</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1silf3c" data-start="241" data-end="278">
<p data-start="244" data-end="278">Selects an image from his computer</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="olv712" data-start="279" data-end="299">
<p data-start="282" data-end="299">Clicks <strong data-start="289" data-end="299">Submit</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="301" data-end="343">👉 Now question: where does that image go?</p>
<h3 data-section-id="14wrjj4" data-start="345" data-end="356">Answer:</h3>
<p data-start="357" data-end="409">It goes from his computer → into your project folder</p>
<hr data-start="411" data-end="414">
<h2 data-section-id="1yt265x" data-start="416" data-end="439">🔹 Real life example</h2>
<p data-start="441" data-end="474">Let’s say your project folder is:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="476" data-end="516"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>C:\xampp\htdocs\news-portal\</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="518" data-end="540">Inside it you created:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="542" data-end="562"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>uploads/</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="564" data-end="603">After upload, image will be saved here:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="605" data-end="662"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>C:\xampp\htdocs\news-portal\uploads\photo.jpg</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="664" data-end="667">
<h2 data-section-id="yvggqz" data-start="669" data-end="706">🔹 What PHP does (in simple words)</h2>
<p data-start="708" data-end="726">PHP does 2 things:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1311l4k" data-start="728" data-end="762">1. Takes the file from browser</h3>
<p data-start="763" data-end="809">When user uploads, PHP receives it temporarily</p>
<h3 data-section-id="otnf5l" data-start="811" data-end="841">2. Moves it to your folder</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="843" data-end="891"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Temporary location → uploads/ folder</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="893" data-end="896">
<h2 data-section-id="2s8n83" data-start="898" data-end="928">🔹 What goes into database?</h2>
<p data-start="930" data-end="974">❌ NOT the image<br data-start="945" data-end="948">
✅ Only the image name/path</p>
<p data-start="976" data-end="984">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="986" data-end="1007"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>photo.jpg</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1009" data-end="1012">
<h2 data-section-id="2e5jas" data-start="1014" data-end="1052">🔹 Then how image shows on website?</h2>
<p data-start="1054" data-end="1072">Your website says:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1074" data-end="1127"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>"Go to uploads folder and show photo.jpg"</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1129" data-end="1132">
<h2 data-section-id="hbpazr" data-start="1134" data-end="1166">🔁 Full flow (very important)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1168" data-end="1343"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Admin selects image</span><br><span>→ Browser sends file to PHP</span><br><span>→ PHP saves file in uploads folder</span><br><span>→ PHP saves file name in database</span><br><span>→ Website reads database</span><br><span>→ Website shows image</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1345" data-end="1348">
<h2 data-section-id="tzbtly" data-start="1350" data-end="1371">🧠 Think like this</h2>
<ul data-start="1373" data-end="1455">
<li data-section-id="bgzvyy" data-start="1373" data-end="1430">
<p data-start="1375" data-end="1430">Database = text storage (headline, content, image name)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="c6s7bt" data-start="1431" data-end="1455">
<p data-start="1433" data-end="1455">Folder = actual images</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1457" data-end="1460">
<h2 data-section-id="im5g0w" data-start="1462" data-end="1499">❓ Why not store image in database?</h2>
<p data-start="1501" data-end="1509">Because:</p>
<ul data-start="1510" data-end="1540">
<li data-section-id="1j4dm33" data-start="1510" data-end="1516">
<p data-start="1512" data-end="1516">Slow</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16odqbv" data-start="1517" data-end="1524">
<p data-start="1519" data-end="1524">Heavy</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9wine6" data-start="1525" data-end="1540">
<p data-start="1527" data-end="1540">Not practical</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1542" data-end="1545">
<h2 data-section-id="1nufjtx" data-start="1547" data-end="1577">🎯 Your understanding check</h2>
<p data-start="1579" data-end="1591">Answer this:</p>
<p data-start="1593" data-end="1640">👉 After upload, where will the image be saved?</p>
<ol data-start="1642" data-end="1688">
<li data-section-id="1kzqb6n" data-start="1642" data-end="1655">
<p data-start="1645" data-end="1655">Database</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1dxa74v" data-start="1656" data-end="1675">
<p data-start="1659" data-end="1675">uploads folder</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xfnx0" data-start="1676" data-end="1688">
<p data-start="1679" data-end="1688">Browser</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1690" data-end="1752">If you answer this correctly, you’ve understood the core idea.</p>
<hr data-start="1754" data-end="1757">
<p data-start="1759" data-end="1785">If still confusing, I can:</p>
<ul data-start="1786" data-end="1855">
<li data-section-id="cy0s7w" data-start="1786" data-end="1802">
<p data-start="1788" data-end="1802">Draw a diagram</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="f01a6z" data-start="1803" data-end="1855">
<p data-start="1805" data-end="1855">Or show super small working example (step-by-step)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1857" data-end="1872" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just tell me 👍</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false"