<p data-start="71" data-end="114">You are already inside phpMyAdmin (good 👍)</p>
<hr data-start="116" data-end="119">
<h2 data-section-id="1oq0467" data-start="121" data-end="154">🔹 Step 1: Go to your database</h2>
<p data-start="156" data-end="190">On the <strong data-start="163" data-end="182">left side panel</strong>, click:</p>
