<p data-start="117" data-end="147">Let me clarify your confusion:</p>
<hr data-start="149" data-end="152">
<h2 data-section-id="ssdxn0" data-start="154" data-end="212">🔹 Why you see “Length = 11” even if you didn’t type it</h2>
<p data-start="214" data-end="230">When you choose:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="232" data-end="254"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Type = INT</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="256" data-end="305">👉 phpMyAdmin <strong data-start="270" data-end="305">automatically fills Length = 11</strong></p>
<p data-start="307" data-end="310">So:</p>
<ul data-start="311" data-end="377">
<li data-section-id="17mhza3" data-start="311" data-end="337">
<p data-start="313" data-end="337">You did NOT write it ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vyjuhy" data-start="338" data-end="377">
<p data-start="340" data-end="377">phpMyAdmin added it automatically ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="379" data-end="382">
<h2 data-section-id="1o4p9rj" data-start="384" data-end="411">🔹 Should you change it?</h2>
<p data-start="413" data-end="447">👉 <strong data-start="416" data-end="447">No. Just leave it as it is.</strong></p>
<p data-start="449" data-end="466">For your project:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="468" data-end="504"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>INT(11) = perfectly fine</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="506" data-end="532">Don’t overthink this part.</p>
<hr data-start="534" data-end="537">
<h2 data-section-id="p698az" data-start="539" data-end="581">🔹 What you SHOULD focus on (important)</h2>
<p data-start="583" data-end="613">For the <code data-start="591" data-end="595">id</code> field, make sure:</p>
<ul data-start="615" data-end="690">
<li data-section-id="caka2j" data-start="615" data-end="631">
<p data-start="617" data-end="631">✅ Type = INT</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bv1pe" data-start="632" data-end="653">
<p data-start="634" data-end="653">✅ Index = PRIMARY</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1na8ksv" data-start="654" data-end="690">
<p data-start="656" data-end="690">✅ A_I (Auto Increment) = checked</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="692" data-end="749">👉 These 3 matter.<br data-start="710" data-end="713">
👉 Length (11) does NOT matter much.</p>
<hr data-start="751" data-end="754">
<h2 data-section-id="1otphu3" data-start="756" data-end="782">🔹 Simple understanding</h2>
<p data-start="784" data-end="800">Think like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="802" data-end="861"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>INT → number type</span><br><span>11 → default setting (ignore)</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="863" data-end="866">
<h2 data-section-id="1ipff0a" data-start="868" data-end="888">🎯 What to do now</h2>
<p data-start="890" data-end="942">Continue creating table without worrying about <code data-start="937" data-end="941">11</code>.</p>
