<h2 data-section-id="nuni4k" data-start="55" data-end="99"><span role="text">🔹 <code data-start="61" data-end="74">news_portal</code> is the <strong data-start="82" data-end="99">database name</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="101" data-end="155">It is the same name you created in phpMyAdmin earlier.</p>
<p data-start="157" data-end="176">Remember this step:</p>
