" data-end="54">Good catch 👀 — that red mark is actually helping you.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="48nma2" data-start="56" data-end="79">🔴 Why the red mark?</h2>
<p data-start="81" data-end="119">Because you <strong data-start="93" data-end="119">forgot a semicolon (;)</strong></p>
<p data-start="121" data-end="162">In PHP, every statement must end with <code data-start="159" data-end="162">;</code></p>
