<h2 data-section-id="eo2omh" data-start="386" data-end="408">🔹 Why this matters</h2>
<p data-start="410" data-end="438">PHP reads code line by line.</p>
<p data-start="440" data-end="503">Without <code data-start="448" data-end="451">;</code>, it doesn’t know where the statement ends → ❌ error</p>
