<h2 data-section-id="cio959" data-start="97" data-end="124"><span role="text">🔹 Why is <code data-start="110" data-end="119">include</code> red?</span></h2>
<p data-start="126" data-end="165">👉 VS Code colors keywords differently.</p>
<ul data-start="167" data-end="280">
<li data-section-id="arkeur" data-start="167" data-end="215">
<p data-start="169" data-end="215"><code data-start="169" data-end="178">include</code> = <strong data-start="181" data-end="196">PHP keyword</strong> → shown in <strong data-start="208" data-end="215">red</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qofhlz" data-start="216" data-end="252">
<p data-start="218" data-end="252"><code data-start="218" data-end="224">echo</code> = keyword → different color</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1spcrfa" data-start="253" data-end="280">
<p data-start="255" data-end="280">variables = another color</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="282" data-end="285">So:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="287" data-end="315"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 