<h2 data-section-id="12fbtxq" data-start="361" data-end="388"><span role="text">🔹 Why is <code data-start="374" data-end="381">&lt;?php</code> white?</span></h2>
<p data-start="390" data-end="416">👉 That’s just your theme.</p>
<p data-start="418" data-end="458">VS Code themes color things differently:</p>
<ul data-start="459" data-end="518">
<li data-section-id="kjwdu8" data-start="459" data-end="491">
<p data-start="461" data-end="491">Some themes make <code data-start="478" data-end="485">&lt;?php</code> white</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17epye4" data-start="492" data-end="518">
<p data-start="494" data-end="518">Some make it purple/blue</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="520" data-end="555">👉 It does <strong data-start="531" data-end="555">NOT affect your code</strong></p>
