<p data-start="655" data-end="682">👉 Takes one news at a time</p>
<hr data-start="684" data-end="687">
<h3 data-section-id="w97enr" data-start="689" data-end="719">4. Displays news on screen</h3>
<p data-start="721" data-end="745">For each news, it shows:</p>
<ul data-start="746" data-end="807">
<li data-section-id="8p3f1q" data-start="746" data-end="758">
<p data-start="748" data-end="758">Headline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qc0833" data-start="759" data-end="768">
<p data-start="761" data-end="768">Image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10tedqr" data-start="769" data-end="786">
<p data-start="771" data-end="786">Short content</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vwowem" data-start="787" data-end="807">
<p data-start="789" data-end="807">“Read More” link</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="809" data-end="812">
<h2 data-section-id="x7a703" data-start="814" data-end="838">🔹 Real-world meaning</h2>
<p data-start="840" data-end="856">Think like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="858" data-end="915"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Database → stores news</span><br><span>index.php → shows news</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="917" data-end="920">
<h2 data-section-id="1lcunlw" data-start="922" data-end="947">🔹 Very simple analogy</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="949" data-end="1008"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>YouTube:</span><br><span>Database = videos</span><br><span>Homepage = index.php</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1010" data-end="1013">
<h2 data-section-id="5fzz1v" data-start="1015" data-end="1049">🔹 Interview answer (important)</h2>
<p data-start="1051" data-end="1063">If they ask:</p>
<p data-start="1065" data-end="1098">👉 “What does your index.php do?”</p>
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1108">You say:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1110" data-end="1327">
<p data-start="1112" data-end="1327">The index.php file acts as the homepage. It connects to the database, retrieves all news records, and displays them dynamically with headline, image, and a short description. Each news item links to a detailed page.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1329" data-end="1332">
<h2 data-section-id="93mmhz" data-start="1334" data-end="1357">🔹 Important concept</h2>
<p data-start="1359" data-end="1393">👉 <code data-start="1362" data-end="1373">index.php</code> is <strong data-start="1377" data-end="1393">dynamic page</strong></p>
<p data-start="1395" data-end="1403">Because:</p>
<ul data-start="1404" data-end="1480">
<li data-section-id="e6285h" data-start="1404" data-end="1433">
<p data-start="1406" data-end="1433">Content comes from database</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tx2a0q" data-start="1434" data-end="1480">
<p data-start="1436" data-end="1480">Changes automatically when new data is added</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1482" data-end="1485">
<h2 data-section-id="yr5u2m" data-start="1487" data-end="1512">🎯 Final understanding</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1514" data-end="1596"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Admin adds news → saved in DB</span><br><span>index.php reads DB → shows news to users</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
