<hr data-start="46" data-end="49">
<h2 data-section-id="1432ci4" data-start="51" data-end="80"><span role="text">🔹 Why <code data-start="61" data-end="79">news_details.php</code>?</span></h2>
<p data-start="82" data-end="90">Because:</p>
<p data-start="92" data-end="189">👉 <code data-start="95" data-end="106">index.php</code> shows <strong data-start="113" data-end="145">only summary (short preview)</strong><br data-start="145" data-end="148">
👉 <code data-start="151" data-end="169">news_details.php</code> shows <strong data-start="176" data-end="189">full news</strong></p>
<hr data-start="191" data-end="194">
<h2 data-section-id="1ozl98a" data-start="196" data-end="227">🔹 Think like a real website</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="wanjmg" data-start="229" data-end="259"><span role="text">On homepage (<code data-start="246" data-end="257">index.php</code>):</span></h3>
<p data-start="261" data-end="270">You show:</p>
<ul data-start="271" data-end="351">
<li data-section-id="8p3f1q" data-start="271" data-end="283">
<p data-start="273" data-end="283">Headline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qc0833" data-start="284" data-end="293">
<p data-start="286" data-end="293">Image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4ql5ih" data-start="294" data-end="328">
<p data-start="296" data-end="328">Short content (100 characters)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5xa4jc" data-start="329" data-end="351">
<p data-start="331" data-end="351">“Read More” button</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="353" data-end="356">
