<h3 data-section-id="a6bkum" data-start="671" data-end="696"><span role="text">2. <code data-start="678" data-end="696">news_details.php</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="698" data-end="739">👉 The page where full news will be shown</p>
<hr data-start="741" data-end="744">
<h3 data-section-id="fet9is" data-start="746" data-end="759"><span role="text">3. <code data-start="753" data-end="759">?id=</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="761" data-end="791">👉 This sends data through URL</p>
<hr data-start="793" data-end="796">
<h3 data-section-id="v7l421" data-start="798" data-end="832"><span role="text">4. <code data-start="805" data-end="832">&lt;?php echo $row['id']; ?&gt;</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="834" data-end="864">👉 Gets the ID of current news</p>
<p data-start="866" data-end="874">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="876" data-end="894"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>id = 7</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="896" data-end="918">So final link becomes:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="920" data-end="953"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>news_details.php?id=7</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="955" data-end="958">
<h2 data-section-id="1266rrk" data-start="960" data-end="986"><span role="text">🔹 Why do we send <code data-start="981" data-end="985">id</code>?</span></h2>
<p data-start="988" data-end="996">Because:</p>
<p data-start="998" data-end="1066">👉 Database has many news<br data-start="1023" data-end="1026">
👉 We need to know <strong data-start="1045" data-end="1066">which one to show</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1068" data-end="1071">
<h2 data-section-id="z3b67q" data-start="1073" data-end="1114"><span role="text">🔹 What happens in <code data-start="1095" data-end="1113">news_details.php</code>?</span></h2>
<p data-start="1116" data-end="1127">It will do:</p>
