<h2 data-section-id="irk8v7" data-start="1501" data-end="1523">🎯 Interview answer</h2>
<p data-start="1525" data-end="1534">If asked:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1536" data-end="1563">
<p data-start="1538" data-end="1563">Why use news_details.php?</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1565" data-end="1573">You say:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1575" data-end="1771">
<p data-start="1577" data-end="1771">Because the homepage shows only a preview of each news item. When the user clicks “Read More”, the news_details.php page receives the news ID and displays the full content of that specific news.</p>
