<h2 data-section-id="83u3oz" data-start="50" data-end="69">🔴 Error meaning</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="71" data-end="126"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>unexpected token "&lt;", expecting end of file</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="128" data-end="142">👉 This means:</p>
<p data-start="144" data-end="251"><strong data-start="144" data-end="251">PHP is still “open”, but you started writing HTML (<code data-start="197" data-end="204">&lt;div&gt;</code>, <code data-start="206" data-end="212">&lt;h2&gt;</code>, etc.) without closing PHP properly.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="253" data-end="256">
<h2 data-section-id="17f576z" data-start="258" data-end="285">🔹 Where your mistake is</h2>
<p data-start="287" data-end="329">From your previous code, you likely wrote:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="331" data-end="465"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼg">include</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"db.php"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"..."</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_query</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$conn</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span>);</span><br><br><span class="ͼg">while</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_fetch_assoc</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span>)) {</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="467" data-end="513">❌ Then directly wrote HTML without closing PHP</p>
<hr data-start="515" data-end="518">
<h2 data-section-id="rf7pg1" data-start="520" data-end="536">✅ Correct way</h2>
<p data-start="538" data-end="580">You must <strong data-start="547" data-end="580">close PHP before writing HTML</strong></p>
<p data-start="582" data-end="592">Like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="594" data-end="957"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼg">include</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"db.php"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"SELECT * FROM news ORDER BY id DESC"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_query</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$conn</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span>);</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼg">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_num_rows</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>) {</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">while</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_fetch_assoc</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span>)) {</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">echo</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'headline'</span><span>]; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span>    }</span><br><br><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">else</span><span> {</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>No news 