<h2 data-section-id="1qyb5mi" data-start="1132" data-end="1161">🔹 Why this error happened</h2>
<p data-start="1163" data-end="1195">You probably did something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1197" data-end="1230"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>while(...) {</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>   ❌</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1270">PHP thinks <code data-start="1243" data-end="1250">&lt;div&gt;</code> is PHP code → error</p>
<hr data-start="1272" data-end="1275">
<h2 data-section-id="df91fk" data-start="1277" data-end="1305">🔥 What you should do now</h2>
<ol data-start="1307" data-end="1446">
<li data-section-id="1qtjhog" data-start="1307" data-end="1332">
<p data-start="1310" data-end="1332">Go to your <code data-start="1321" data-end="1332">index.php</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i7d9ns" data-start="1333" data-end="1407">
<p data-start="1336" data-end="1346">Make sure:</p>
<ul data-start="1350" data-end="1407">
<li data-section-id="eky9qh" data-start="1350" data-end="1369">
<p data-start="1352" data-end="1369">Every <code data-start="1358" data-end="1361">{</code> has <code data-start="1366" data-end="1369">}</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wpr8vl" data-start="1373" data-end="1407">
<p data-start="1375" data-end="1407">You close PHP before HTML (<code data-start="1402" data-end="1406">?&gt;</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1imw35z" data-start="1408" data-end="1446">
<p data-start="1411" data-end="1446">Follow the correct structure I gave</p>
</li>
</ol>
