<h1 data-section-id="4gdsws" data-start="232" data-end="278">🔹 1. Use Proper Formatting (VERY IMPORTANT)</h1>
<p data-start="280" data-end="308">Rewrite your code like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="310" data-end="1117"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼg">include</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"db.php"</span><span>;</span><br><br><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"SELECT * FROM news ORDER BY id DESC"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_query</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$conn</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼm">$query</span><span>);</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;title&gt;</span><span>News Portal</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span>Latest News</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_num_rows</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>): </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">while</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">mysqli_fetch_assoc</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$result</span><span>)): </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"news-box"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'headline'</span><span>]; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">if</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼg">!</span><span class="ͼm">empty</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'image'</span><span>])): </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">src</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"uploads/</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'image'</span><span>]; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span class="ͼk">"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">width</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"250"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">endif</span><span>; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;p&gt;</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">substr</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'content'</span><span>], </span><span class="ͼj">0</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼj">100</span><span>); </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span>...</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span>            </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;a</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">href</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"news_details.php?id=</span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼm">$row</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼk">'id'</span><span>]; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><span class="ͼk">"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><span>Read More</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">endwhile</span><span>; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">else</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>No news found</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">endif</span><span>; </span><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/html&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
