<h2 data-section-id="54ucpt" data-start="39" data-end="58">Create this file</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="60" data-end="90"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>admin/add_news.php</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="92" data-end="129">This is where your employer will add:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="131" data-end="165"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Headline</span><br><span>Image</span><br><span>Content</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h2 data-section-id="1qpehfy" data-start="167" data-end="201">Step 1: Create basic form first</h2>
<p data-start="203" data-end="238">Write this in <code data-start="217" data-end="237">admin/add_news.php</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="240" data-end="764"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼg">include</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"../db.php"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;title&gt;</span><span>Add News</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span>Add News</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;form</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">method</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"POST"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">enctype</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"multipart/form-data"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;label&gt;</span><span>Headline</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"text"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"headline"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;label&gt;</span><span>Image</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"file"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"image"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;label&gt;</span><span>Content</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;textarea</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"content"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rows</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"6"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">cols</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"50"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;button</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">type</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"submit"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">name</span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span class="ͼk">"submit"</span><span class="ͼo">&gt;</span><span>Add News</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/form&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/html&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h2 data-section-id="1x59eh9" data-start="766" data-end="783">Important line</h2>
