<hr data-start="1121" data-end="1124">
<h3 data-section-id="17zxjht" data-start="1126" data-end="1144">3. Query runs:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1146" data-end="1188"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>SQL</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼg">SELECT</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">FROM</span><span> news </span><span class="ͼg">WHERE</span><span> id </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">1</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1212">👉 Gets only that news</p>
<hr data-start="1214" data-end="1217">
<h3 data-section-id="uvr6h1" data-start="1219" data-end="1237">4. Page shows:</h3>
<ul data-start="1238" data-end="1282">
<li data-section-id="hryp19" data-start="1238" data-end="1255">
<p data-start="1240" data-end="1255">Full headline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f2yxgy" data-start="1256" data-end="1272">
<p data-start="1258" data-end="1272">Full content</p>
</li>
