</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1284" data-end="1287">
<h1 data-section-id="yc9okp" data-start="1289" data-end="1301">🔹 Test it</h1>
<p data-start="1303" data-end="1341">Click <strong data-start="1309" data-end="1322">Read More</strong> from your homepage</p>
<p data-start="1343" data-end="1355">OR manually:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1357" data-end="1419"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>http://localhost/news_portal/news_details.php?id=1</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1421" data-end="1424">
<h1 data-section-id="167l76m" data-start="1426" data-end="1446">🔥 Important check</h1>
<p data-start="1448" data-end="1477">If page shows error or blank:</p>
<ul data-start="1479" data-end="1582">
<li data-section-id="rnmh9z" data-start="1479" data-end="1510">
<p data-start="1481" data-end="1510">Make sure <code data-start="1491" data-end="1495">id</code> exists in DB</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zve6s4" data-start="1511" data-end="1540">
<p data-start="1513" data-end="1540">Make sure URL has <code data-start="1531" data-end="1538">?id=1</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wdockh" data-start="1541" data-end="1582">
<p data-start="1543" data-end="1582">Make sure no typo in <code data-start="1564" data-end="1582">$row['headline']</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1584" data-end="1587">
<h1 data-section-id="lra6th" data-start="1589" data-end="1609">🎯 After this step</h1>
<p data-start="1611" data-end="1641">Now your frontend is complete:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1643" data-end="1700"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>index.php → list</span><br><span>news_details.php → full view</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1702" data-end="1705">
<h1 data-section-id="1ihqog3" data-start="1707" data-end="1733">🚀 NEXT (very important)</h1>
<p data-start="1735" data-end="1791">Now we move to the <strong data-start="1754" data-end="1790">main feature your employer wants</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="1793" data-end="1848">👉 <code data-start="1796" data-end="1816">admin/add_news.php</code><br data-start="1816" data-end="1819">
(so he can push news himself)</p>
<hr data-start="1850" data-end="1853">
<p data-start="1855" data-end="1863">Tell me:</p>
