flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼg">SELECT</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">FROM</span><span> news </span><span class="ͼg">WHERE</span><span> id </span><span class="ͼg">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼj">3</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="677" data-end="704">👉 Only one row is returned</p>
<hr data-start="706" data-end="709">
<h3 data-section-id="12s2nhy" data-start="711" data-end="736">4. Displays full data</h3>
