<h2 data-section-id="1ain5dr" data-start="117" data-end="139">🔹 What does it do?</h2>
<p data-start="141" data-end="174">👉 It <strong data-start="147" data-end="173">gets data from the URL</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="176" data-end="179">
<h2 data-section-id="rh5w3t" data-start="181" data-end="194">🔹 Example</h2>
<p data-start="196" data-end="211">If your URL is:</p>
