<p data-start="41" data-end="91">is not PHP—it’s <strong data-start="57" data-end="65">HTML</strong>, and it’s very important.</p>
<hr data-start="93" data-end="96">
<h2 data-section-id="1ain5dr" data-start="98" data-end="120">🔹 What does it do?</h2>
<p data-start="122" data-end="146">👉 It tells the browser:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="148" data-end="184"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>"This document is HTML5"</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="186" data-end="189">
<h2 data-section-id="1coyw52" data-start="191" data-end="215">🔹 Why do we need it?</h2>
<p data-start="217" data-end="245">Without it, the browser may:</p>
<ul data-start="246" data-end="300">
<li data-section-id="n2iyj5" data-start="246" data-end="275">
<p data-start="248" data-end="275">Render page incorrectly ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="28hilc" data-start="276" data-end="300">
<p data-start="278" data-end="300">Use old HTML rules ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="302" data-end="310">With it:</p>
<ul data-start="311" data-end="353">
<li data-section-id="6r0dp9" data-start="311" data-end="330">
<p data-start="313" data-end="330">Proper layout ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rxqqnu" data-start="331" data-end="353">
<p data-start="333" data-end="353">Modern standards ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="355" data-end="358">
<h2 data-section-id="vyikw0" data-start="360" data-end="385">🔹 Where should it be?</h2>
<p data-start="387" data-end="429">👉 Always at the <strong data-start="404" data-end="429">very top of your page</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="431" data-end="514"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Edit"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href