 flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼo">&lt;title&gt;</span><span>My Page</span><span class="ͼo">&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;body&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="516" data-end="519">
<h2 data-section-id="l4zcd5" data-start="521" data-end="543">🔹 In your PHP file</h2>
<p data-start="545" data-end="563">You usually write:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="565" data-end="626"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>PHP</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span class="ͼf">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="ͼe">// PHP logic here</span><br><span class="ͼf">?&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼf">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼo">&lt;html&gt;</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="628" data-end="659">👉 PHP first → then HTML starts</p>
<hr data-start="661" data-end="664">
<h2 data-section-id="1ew0onw" data-start="666" data-end="686">🔹 Simple analogy</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="688" data-end="752"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; = telling browser the language rules</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="754" data-end="757">
<h2 data-section-id="irk8v7" data-start="759" data-end="781">🎯 Interview answer</h2>
<p data-start="783" data-end="792">If asked:</p>
<blockquote data-start="794" data-end="820">
<p data-start="796" data-end="820">What is &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;?</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="822" data-end="830">You say:</p>
<blockquote data-start="832" data-end="927">
<p data-start="834" data-end="927">It declares the document type and tells the browser to render the page using HTML5 standards.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="929" data-end="932">
<h2 data-section-id="b0yae6" data-start="934" data-end="951">🔥 Quick check</h2>
