<p data-start="133" data-end="150">👉 PHP is saying:</p>
<blockquote data-start="152" data-end="220">
<p data-start="154" data-end="220">“I tried to get <code data-start="170" data-end="183">$_GET['id']</code>, but <code data-start="189" data-end="193">id</code> is not present in the URL”</p>
