ta-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="99dfdab8-a26a-4843-8e33-ab57995f3850" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="59">Short answer: <strong data-start="14" data-end="59">yes—but only if you use it the right way.</strong></p>
<p data-start="61" data-end="195">Right now you’re <em data-start="78" data-end="96">not just copying</em>—you’re asking “why”, fixing errors, and understanding line by line. That’s the <strong data-start="176" data-end="192">correct path</strong> 👍</p>
<hr data-start="197" data-end="200">
<h2 data-section-id="eh3h5c" data-start="202" data-end="237">🔹 The wrong way (don’t do this)</h2>
<ul data-start="239" data-end="313">
<li data-section-id="19oun77" data-start="239" data-end="257">
<p data-start="241" data-end="257">Copy full code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ni04km" data-start="258" data-end="270">
<p data-start="260" data-end="270">Paste it</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15x1b53" data-start="271" data-end="283">
<p data-start="273" data-end="283">It works</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="g7yqd" data-start="284" data-end="313">
<p data-start="286" data-end="313">You don’t know how or why</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="315" data-end="362">👉 In interview, you’ll get stuck immediately ❌</p>
<hr data-start="364" data-end="367">
<h2 data-section-id="5z9fyk" data-start="369" data-end="412">🔹 The right way (what you’re doing now)</h2>
<ul data-start="414" data-end="500">
<li data-section-id="1m1ftnc" data-start="414" data-end="428">
<p data-start="416" data-end="428">Write code</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="itco2v" data-start="429" data-end="456">
<p data-start="431" data-end="456">Ask what each line does</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6zegxl" data-start="457" data-end="480">
<p data-start="459" data-end="480">Fix errors yourself</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19i8ou6" data-start="481" data-end="500">
<p data-start="483" data-end="500">Understand flow</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="502" data-end="544">👉 This builds <strong data-start="517" data-end="542">real backend thinking</strong> ✅</p>
<hr data-start="546" data-end="549">
<h2 data-section-id="o2ddup" data-start="551" data-end="585">🔹 Best method (very important)</h2>
<p data-start="587" data-end="608">Use this 3-step rule:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1bfqfxt" data-start="610" data-end="628">1. See / Learn</h3>
<p data-start="629" data-end="660">Understand the code (with help)</p>
<h3 data-section-id="e5a6vh" data-start="662" data-end="685">2. Close everything</h3>
<p data-start="686" data-end="704">Don’t look at code</p>
<h3 data-section-id="or93ba" data-start="706" data-end="732">3. Rewrite from memory</h3>
<p data-start="734" data-end="799">👉 If you can rewrite → you learned it<br data-start="772" data-end="775">
👉 If not → review again</p>
<hr data-start="801" data-end="804">
<h2 data-section-id="4kol12" data-start="806" data-end="851">🔹 Your current behavior (honest feedback)</h2>
<p data-start="853" data-end="861">You are:</p>
<ul data-start="862" data-end="938">
<li data-section-id="xc3ya2" data-start="862" data-end="889">
<p data-start="864" data-end="889">Asking good questions ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ah6y9c" data-start="890" data-end="912">
<p data-start="892" data-end="912">Debugging errors ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t1tbb" data-start="913" data-end="938">
<p data-start="915" data-end="938">Understanding logic ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="940" data-end="996">👉 This is <strong data-start="951" data-end="966">not copying</strong>. This is <strong data-start="976" data-end="995">guided learning</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="998" data-end="1001">
<h2 data-section-id="1wmhe8b" data-start="1003" data-end="1040">🔹 What interviewers actually test</h2>
<p data-start="1042" data-end="1046">Not:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1047" data-end="1082"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Do you remember syntax?</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1084" data-end="1088">But:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1089" data-end="1137"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Can you explain what your code does?</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1139" data-end="1142">
<h2 data-section-id="tpshkl" data-start="1144" data-end="1167">🔹 Real test for you</h2>
