<h3 data-section-id="1lbd6r3" data-start="320" data-end="336">Explanation:</h3>
<ul data-start="337" data-end="453">
<li data-section-id="1x75vkc" data-start="337" data-end="371">
<p data-start="339" data-end="371"><code data-start="339" data-end="347">$_POST</code> → gets data from form</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tg76iv" data-start="372" data-end="408">
<p data-start="374" data-end="408"><code data-start="374" data-end="384">'submit'</code> → name of your button</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b2z1uz" data-start="409" data-end="453">
<p data-start="411" data-end="453"><code data-start="411" data-end="420">isset()</code> → checks if form was submitted</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="455" data-end="466">👉 Meaning:</p>
<blockquote data-start="467" data-end="513">
<p data-start="469" data-end="513">“Run this code only when user clicks submit”</p>
</blockquote>
