<p data-start="272" data-end="300">👉 This is required because:</p>
<ul data-start="301" data-end="377">
<li data-section-id="az1co0" data-start="301" data-end="329">
<p data-start="303" data-end="329"><code data-start="303" data-end="309">POST</code> → sends text data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x3gsem" data-start="330" data-end="377">
<p data-start="332" data-end="377"><code data-start="332" data-end="353">multipart/form-data</code> → allows image upload</p>
</li>
</ul>
