<h2 data-section-id="1v7qi3j" data-start="268" data-end="303">🔴 2. HTML structure (important)</h2>
<p data-start="305" data-end="364">Your <code data-start="310" data-end="327">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code> and <code data-start="332" data-end="340">&lt;html&gt;</code> are in the wrong place.</p>
<p data-start="366" data-end="425">👉 They should be at the <strong data-start="391" data-end="398">top</strong>, not inside the container.</p>
<hr data-start="427" data-end="430">
