<hr data-start="873" data-end="876">
<h2 data-section-id="1vajsqr" data-start="878" data-end="923">🔥 Why your form still looked slightly off</h2>
<ul data-start="925" data-end="1051">
<li data-section-id="1deck0q" data-start="925" data-end="968">
<p data-start="927" data-end="968">Wrong <code data-start="933" data-end="942">enctype</code> → image upload may fail</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="48dqo8" data-start="969" data-end="1009">
<p data-start="971" data-end="1009">Inputs not full width → looks uneven</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nhyzrz" data-start="1010" data-end="1051">
<p data-start="1012" data-end="1051">HTML structure mixed → unprofessional</p>
</li>
</ul>
