<h2 data-section-id="kub8yd" data-start="99" data-end="117">❌ What’s wrong?</h2>
<p data-start="119" data-end="196">👉 <code data-start="122" data-end="140">mysqli_connect()</code> is used to <strong data-start="152" data-end="175">connect to database</strong>, not to run queries.</p>
