arkdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="109">That popup is <strong data-start="14" data-end="36">NOT from your code</strong> 👍<br data-start="39" data-end="42">
It’s coming from a <strong data-start="61" data-end="108">browser extension (SaveFrom / OrangeMonkey)</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="111" data-end="114">
<h2 data-section-id="19jo9t" data-start="116" data-end="132">🔴 What it is</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="134" data-end="185"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>SaveFrom.net Helper → browser extension</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="187" data-end="256">👉 It injects scripts into pages<br data-start="219" data-end="222">
👉 That’s why you see this message</p>
<hr data-start="258" data-end="261">
<h2 data-section-id="1a1ae4u" data-start="263" data-end="282">✅ How to stop it</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="7ohuee" data-start="284" data-end="325">🔹 Option 1: Disable extension (best)</h3>
<ol data-start="327" data-end="353">
<li data-section-id="dn8yi8" data-start="327" data-end="343">
<p data-start="330" data-end="343">Open Chrome</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1dn431s" data-start="344" data-end="353">
<p data-start="347" data-end="353">Go to:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="354" data-end="386"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-430d4e28.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>chrome://extensions/</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="3" data-start="387" data-end="395">
<li data-section-id="13gyexz" data-start="387" data-end="395">
<p data-start="390" data-end="395">Find:</p>
