<h2 data-section-id="1eq4eq" data-start="230" data-end="247">🔹 Explanation</h2>
<ul data-start="249" data-end="382">
<li data-section-id="1marbj5" data-start="249" data-end="298">
<p data-start="251" data-end="298"><code data-start="251" data-end="264">width: 100%</code> → takes full width of container</p>
